    <h1>Your Rights at Home</h1>
    <p class="lede">Your home receives the strongest protection under the Fourth Amendment. As a general rule, law enforcement needs a warrant signed by a judge to enter your home.</p>
    <p class="updated">Updated as of April 30, 2026</p>
  </div>
</section>

